description:
We’re introducing the new ParkSimply 2.0 app, which offers a simple and convenient way to pay for parking in cities, parking garages, hospitals, and car parks across the Czech Republic.

ParkSimply 2.0 is the only app that provides the widest range of payment methods — Apple Pay, credit/debit card, Premium SMS, and mobile payment (m-platba) — quickly, securely, and without unnecessary stress, especially when you're rushing to a meeting or appointment.

Key features:
Even simpler user interface — with ParkSimply 2.0, you’ll pay faster than with any other app on the Czech market;
No account registration required — we make it quicker for you;
New payment options: Apple Pay, VISA and Mastercard, Premium SMS, and m-platba;
Improved map backgrounds — choose from several map types;
Tax receipts are available immediately after payment directly in the app — no need to search for them later;
No need to worry about fines or towing — our system instantly confirms your parking payment;
Notifications before your parking expires;
And many more features to come — every month we’ll add a new one. Get involved and help improve the app: send us your feedback or vote on new features;
We don’t want to overwhelm you from the start — that’s why we’ll add new features gradually, one each month.
